title: Big Folks & Bandman Kevo on 16ShotEm Beef, Chicago Politics, Baby Mama Drama & More
description:
Flakko coming through with the messiness, bringing Kevo and his manager Big Folks to give their side of the whole 16 beef, their perspectives on Chicago rappers, politics, BBL, and much more!

-----
00:00 Intro
2:01 Got plugged with the GDs in 1993
2:58 Beating a double m*rder case at 18, sh*t his kidnappers in the head
6:30 Folks got sh*t 6 times in 2006, being fat literally saved his life
11:15 Lil Mouse was one of the first artists Folks worked with
14:13 Did Slim Jesus take Lil Mouse shine? Lil Mouse x Slim Jesus beef
17:10 Folks was super close with Zacktv, says he wasn't from Chicago and made the mistakes of choosing sides, warns Billy Kauck to watch his step
23:10 Folks confirms that Rick Ross has stolen Birdman's whole persona
26:57 A group of Mexican ran down to the tour bus and stabbed Nipsey's right-hand man
29:58 Drake and Future, were never scared to come to the hood, Drake pulled up without security
30:29 Meek says he wanna go to Durk's hood, Durk says "at your own risk"
32:25 Folks said he was entertained by the Flakko 16 interview, Kevo calls him a P again
36:36 Folks is the one who said 16 can't go to Chicago
36:54 It all started on IG live with Kevo and 16
41:50 Folks says 16 is obsessed with Kevo, and his ex-girlfriend wanted to plot on Kevo
43:00 Kevo says he used her while he was locked up to hold him down but she was nothing else, says he married her as a favor
49:18 Kevo says she went on Say Cheese to expose him because he didn't wanna be with her anymore
51:20 Folks says Rooga allegedly called him to distance himself from 16
53:00 Kevo on the BBL accusation
55:30 Kevo calls 16 a T
1:01:46 Kevo tries to explain that he never paid vlogs to post dirt on 16
1:06:30 Only Fans scamming allegations
1:08:20 Kevo relationship with Miko
1:10:25 Kevo smashing Kayla Nicole, says it is ancient history
1:19:02 Is TeeJay6x still tryna scam people?
1:22:39 Folks says he didn't know Rooga was a GD
1:23:46 Folks says Kanye is a real GD
1:25:18 Durk's dad did 30 years for not snitching
1:34:05 Folks connected to BMF
1:34:09 Kevo and Folks pull out 16 personal information and alleged cases
1:43:20 Kevo and Folks say they will never make amends with 16
1:45:41 Folks brings a couple of his artists
1:51:36 Folks reacts to Ch. White and 600 Brizzy situation
-----
